  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Warehouse Assistant (Forklift)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a Government link company in the FMCG industry. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Warehouse Assistant to be part of their Warehouse team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the West.</strong></p><p><br /><strong>Job Responsibilities of Warehouse Assistant:</strong></p><ul><li>Receive, check quantity & quality, and sort incoming goods.</li><li>Store items neatly and accessibly in the warehouse.</li><li>Pick and pack items for delivery based on requests.</li><li>Maintain accurate records of inventory and stock locations.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess Forklift License</li><li>Min 1 - 2 years of relevant experience</li><li>Comfortable to work during weekends (5 days work week)</li></ul><p></p><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</li><li>EA License No. 19C9682</li><li>EA Reg. No. R22108850 (Chan Mun Mun)</li></ul>",
